descriptionAbout: Welcome to Dijk9! In the center of the City of Light, or in the heart of Eindhoven, wine and food go hand in hand at Dijk9. Add to that the Brabant atmosphere and your evening will be great again! When the weather is nice, you can sit on the lovely terrace and enjoy a refreshing drink and specialties from French-international cuisine! You can find Dijk9 at Stratumsedijk 9 in Eindhoven.
